trans-unit.target: Geeft de stijl van de tabel legenda.

trans-unit.source: The legend table style is automatically determined by the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: De stijl van de tabel legenda wordt automatisch bepaald door de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart"> </xref> besturingselement.

trans-unit.source: Legend items will be fit vertically within the legend.
trans-unit.target: Legenda-items worden verticaal past binnen de legenda.

trans-unit.source: This style is preferred when <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref> is set to <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Deze stijl wordt aanbevolen wanneer <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref> is ingesteld op <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref> of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Legend items will be fit horizontally within the legend.
trans-unit.target: Legenda-items worden horizontaal past binnen de legenda.

trans-unit.source: This style is preferred when <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref> is set to <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Deze stijl wordt aanbevolen wanneer <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref> is ingesteld op <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref> of <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Docking"> </xref>.
